summary:
- **Stop Loss Trigger Event**: CitiFirst MINI ZHGKOT (COPPER FUTURE Sep-2025) suspended due to underlying parcel price hitting Stop Loss Level of **5.4400**.  
- **Trading Window**: Bid at Cash Amount will be displayed from **2pm 9 Jul 2025 to 4pm 10 Jul 2025**. Holders can sell to Citi during this window.  
- **Automatic Payout**: Unsold MINIs will be terminated, with holders receiving Stop Loss Amount within **10 business days** post-suspension.
